#all about class 5🎶🎶😉
#linear regression
#data

#X(Week)                           Y(sales in thousand)
#________________________________________________________
#1                                      1.2
#2                                      1.8
#3                                      2.5
#4                                      3.2
#5                                      3.8

#linear regression formula ---> y=a0+a1*x

#a1 --->((Mean of(x*y))-(x*y))/(mean of(x^2))-(mean of(x)^2)
#a0=mean(y)-al*meanof(x)


#                  x             y                      x^2                    x^y
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#                  1            1.2                      1                     1.2
#                  2            1.8                      4                     3.6
#                  3            2.5                      9                     7.5
#                  4            3.2                      16                    12.8
#                  5            3.8                      25                    19
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#             sum:15           12.5                      55                    44.4
#         average:3             2.5                      11                     8.88
            
    
#1.)x=3          y=2.5     mean(x^2)=11       meanof(xy)=8.88
#a1=(8.88-(3*2.52))//11-3^2 ==>0.66
#a0=2.52-(0.66*3)=0.54


#the sales of 3rd week
#y=a0+(a1*x)
#y=0.54+(0.66*3)
#y=2.25

#the sales of 7th week 
#y=0.54+(0.66*7)
#y=5.16
